Persevere-Client version 0.3
=============================

This is a module for interacting with the Persevere JSON Database, which Supports REST Database interactions, and comet updates.

version 0.2 addes the propSet method, and deleteById method, to allow for updating objects 

version 0.3 provides package naming and version cleanup

version 0.31 fixes perldoc for Persevere::Client::Class

The examples directory has complete functional examples that show full usage of this module

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

JSON
LWP::UserAgent
HTTP:Rquest
HTTP::Status
HTTP::Headers
HTTP::Response
HTTP::Cookies

